==Galician==
===Alternative forms=== * {{l|gl|muito}}
===Etymology=== From {{etyl|la|gl}} {{term|multus|lang=la}}.
===Adjective=== {{gl-adj|f=moita}}
# [[much]], [[many]], [[a lot]] of, [[lots of]] #: '''''Moita''' xente vive neste edificio.'' #:: '''''Many''' people live in this building.'' #: ''O meu avó construíu '''moitas''' casas nos anos setenta.'' #:: ''My grandfather built '''lots of''' houses in the seventies.''
===Adverb=== {{gl-adv}}
# [[much]], [[a lot]] (of), [[lots]] #: ''Non teño '''moito''' diñeiro.'' #:: ''I don't have '''a lot''' of money.'' #: ''Traballa '''moito''' menos ca min.'' #:: ''He works '''much''' less than I do.'' #: ''Ela corre '''moito'''.'' #:: ''She runs '''a lot'''.''
====Antonyms==== * {{l|gl|pouco}}
===Pronoun=== {{head|gl|pronoun}}
# [[much]], [[a lot]] {{gloss|a large amount or a great extent}} #: ''Seu irmán nunca ten '''moito''' que dicir.'' #:: ''His brother never has '''much''' to say.''
====Antonyms==== * {{l|gl|pouco}}
====Related terms==== * {{l|gl|moi}}
