==Galician== ===Alternative forms=== * [[nosoutras]] {{g|f}}
===Etymology=== From {{term|nós|lang=gl}} + {{term|outros|lang=gl}}.
===Pronoun=== {{gl-pron|form=nom|g=m|dat=nos|acc=nos}}
# [[we]], [[us]] (''plural first-person personal pronoun'')
====Usage notes==== The form ''nosoutros'' or ''nós'' is used as the subject of a sentence or as the object of a preposition. The unaccented form ''nos'' is used as the direct or indirect object.
====Synonyms==== * {{sense|we, us}} [[nós]]
